Overview

This dashboard shows File and URL overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested File and URL logs from Prisma Access.

It highlights the top actions performed by the firewall, identifies the top applications associated with URLs, and lists the most blocked files. It also shows the top URL categories and the top URLs used in web requests. Additionally, the dashboard provides insights into the top source users accessing these URLs. For further analysis, it includes URL events by web browser and essential details of both file and URL events.
